<!--T:2-->
'''Badges''' are icons that appear on a user's profile to signify their contributions to the platform.

== Lists of badges == <!--T:3-->

=== Individual badges === <!--T:4-->

<!--T:5-->
The following badges only have a single tier, which is to either have the badge or not. They are often used to signify contributions or involvement, but can also reflect a current temporary state, such as the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] badge.

